title: Ep. 149 "Who Raised You"
description:
This week it's just us again and we're discussing how your relationship with your parents can really affect your love life.

Please support our non-profit partner FUND TEXAS CHOICE when you purchase your tickets to the live show. there is a donation box on the ticket page.
